      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "Keen to be with LET IT BEEL (2) who ran a most encouraging race first up at Sandown Hillside over 1300m, getting home strongly for third in what looks a stronger maiden than this. He was knocking on the door in better company last time in as well and sets up perfectly from the gate. Rates as the one to beat. PASIFAE (9) resumes having run in a good 2yo race on debut at Ballarat when fourth. She was big odds there but can be improved this time around with gear changes made. SALARAE (5) has run fourth in both starts to date, just struggling to get into a race dominated up on speed last time. She can be an improver. WRITTEN STORY (6) didn't fire fresh but that was a strong maiden at Pakenham and she can do better. ZOUDEADLY (3) next best.",
